com.kilpatrickaudio.elmGen
Class ElmProgram

java.lang.Object
  com.kilpatrickaudio.elmGen.ElmProgram
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bypass, Distortion, Mute, Reverb
public class ElmProgram
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a program on the DSP. Effect programs should subclass this class and call the appropriate methods to set up and test the program.

Author:
andrew

ElmProgram

public ElmProgram(java.lang.String name)
Creates a new SpinProgram with a blank memory map and instruction list. The default samplerate is 32768Hz.

Parameters:
name - the program name

writeRegisterLowshelf

public void writeRegisterLowshelf(int addr,
                                  double scale)

Parameters:
addr - the register to use
scale - the amount to scale the result before adding PACC
